sub_title: English Language Expert – Editor, Writer, Dutch-to-English Translator
summary: I am an editor, writer and Dutch-to-English translator in the Netherlands with more than 15 years experience helping businesses and individuals communicate more clearly in English. Whether you are an entrepreneur who needs an English webpage, a professor with an article to edit or a professional writing for an international audience, I can help you make your text sound like it was written by a native English speaker.
